TEPEDINO--Vincent M. on January 13, 2007. Founder of Tepedino & Company, a certified public accounting firm located in Garden City, NY. Generously gave of his time and talents to many charitable and educational organizations. He served on many corporate and philantropic boards. Beloved husband of the late Jean, loving father of Carol Ann O'Donnell, Robert Tepedino and the late Vincent Jr. Cherished grandfather of Vincent, Megan and Amanda. Dear father-in-law of Dennis and Madeline. Fond brother of Dr. Michael and Marylee Tepedino. Also survived by many nieces and nephews. Reposing at Fredrick J. Chapey & Sons Bethpage Funeral Home, 20 Hicksville Road (1 mile north of Southern State Pkwy, exit 29). Visitation Monday, 2-4:30 and 7-9:30pm. Celebration of the liturgy of Christian burial, 11:00am at St. Agnes Cathedral, Rockville Centre. Interment Evergreen Cemetery, Brooklyn. Memorial contributions may be sent to Homes for Autistic Children and Adults, 585 Stewart Ave. Garden City, NY 11530.
